Cell["\<\
The above ZZ interaction is equivalent to the following combination of CNOT \
and single-qubit rotation:\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->248952008,ExpressionUUID->"6abcb79a-a3d0-4c26-b9ee-b61762a87532"],

